		<p style='background: rgb(221,221,221);padding: 0.04cm 0.14cm; text-indent: 0cm; margin-right: 1cm;  margin-bottom: 0cm;'>ActiveRecordBrowser is a Ruby on Rails plugin that offers the
controlling function of the table over the Internet.

Currently it can create add/delete/edit data . And data can be
imported to the database, and can be exported too by CSV file.</p><br />
